    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Metal receptacles of a standardized volume, sealable and suitable for re-use, designed to be stacked and secured together for shipping. These are suited to various modes of transport including marine, railroad, and trucking.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
